highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “DAISIES” is the highest at #3.
“Rather Be (feat. Jess Glynne)” by Clean Bandit and Jess Glynne is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #134.
“Sweater Weather” by The Neighbourhood has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 1768 days straight.
“POR SUS BESOS” by Tito Double P is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 140 spots at #32.
